API server: Enabled / Disabled   
Audit: Enabled / Disabled   
Authenticator: Enabled / Disabled  
Controller manager: Enabled / Disabled  
Scheduler: Enabled / Disabled  
 
4. Ensure that all options are set to 'Enabled'.  
